title: BeOS R5.1 (Dano)
description:
This is BeOS R5.1 (Dano). To install Dano, you must do the following:

Make a separate partition on your hard drive.
Burn the ISO image to a CD.
Open the BeOS installer.
Choose the BeOS Dano CD for the install media.
Install onto the empty partition.

Use the steps provided to start enjoying BeOS R5.1 Dano.

Remember to seed when you are done downloading!

-CG701
